formattedAddress: SAFRA Toa Payoh (293 Lorong 6 Toa Payoh)

tip.text: Only the crab beehoon stands out! The rest of the Zi char dishes are just mediocre!
Tried the 7 in 1 set meal at $28++ per person. Not that fantastic n value for money. The Chinese Walter sound discouraging when u order this set. Lol! They keep asking you to try the ala carte menu.
Mee Hoon Kway n Sheng mien are the most popular here! Close on Wednesday n Thursday! Open till 2.30 pm.
Tenderloin steak n fried chicken wing are my all times fav here!
